{"id": 2435, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x瓶装星冰乐】讲道理，有没有哪些理由让你暗戳戳期待夏天？", "description": "西瓜！！短裙！！大长腿！！还有爽到爆的瓶装星冰乐！", "record_count": 10544, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180628174123FXN2e1vbIAfGukz7.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-04T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 290820, "content": "空调凉风", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700429}, {"id": 290566, "content": "夏日必备么？星冰乐呀！", "image": null, "praise_count": 585, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 290567, "content": "大腿 性躁动 满身大汗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1264, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272328}, {"id": 290568, "content": "季节性鼻炎，冬天犯病，夏天痊愈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305197}, {"id": 290569, "content": "前段时间好奇心还说民众关注健康，星冰乐越来越不好卖，今天就......我不会说我的夏天就为了吃星冰乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 209, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798290}, {"id": 290570, "content": "当然是期待舌尖与冰凉饮品的味蕾碰撞啦～", "image": null, "praise_count": 195, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390427}, {"id": 290826, "content": "今年的世界杯，漂亮的耳饰，提着很轻的行李出行…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278935}, {"id": 290571, "content": "讲真，在广州的我其实都在暗戳戳的期待冬季。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 414, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334651}, {"id": 290827, "content": "花花，华晨宇的演唱会！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278935}, {"id": 290572, "content": "心静自然凉", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905765}, {"id": 290573, "content": "空调 空调 空调 重要的事情说三遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787196}, {"id": 290574, "content": "毕竟加拿大除了夏天另外三个季节是”Almost winter”, “Winter”, 和”Still winter”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 481, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390431}, {"id": 290575, "content": "西瓜??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1122, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 985292}, {"id": 291855, "content": "暑假 海边 冰棍儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395241}, {"id": 290576, "content": "当学生的时候期待暑假，毕业了还是喜欢秋天?", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 290577, "content": "一边是金色阳光、一边是绿色树荫，在蓝色的泳池里各种游来游去～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847412}, {"id": 290578, "content": "夏天短裙真的会显腿长啊，最喜欢别人夸了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 519, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572462}, {"id": 290580, "content": "如果不提星冰乐厂商会不会很尴尬～", "image": null, "praise_count": 233, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724535}, {"id": 290581, "content": "各种冰激凌…而且夏天喝冰镇雪碧是真的爽！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 427, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920529}, {"id": 290582, "content": "宁静的夏天，天空中繁星点点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288140}, {"id": 293398, "content": "烈日下看大长腿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407012}, {"id": 290583, "content": "别人休息我在实习，希望自己能变强吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 144, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 84181}, {"id": 290586, "content": "吹不上空调的什么都没有。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179165}, {"id": 290587, "content": "马上就到冬天了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1385458}, {"id": 290588, "content": "蝉叫 西瓜 短裙", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288801}, {"id": 290589, "content": "估计是小龙虾吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 208, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352265}, {"id": 290590, "content": "各种小姐姐好看下衣服都看不够呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 376, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390468}, {"id": 290591, "content": "沙滩 星冰乐 火烈鸟漂浮圈 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 243, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449854}, {"id": 290592, "content": "掀开瓶盖，冰咖啡接触到嘴唇的前一秒，感受到冷气的一瞬间，特别是对星冰乐冰爽口感的那种期待", "image": null, "praise_count": 307, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849983}, {"id": 290593, "content": "在没有毕业前，我对夏天的期待是“漫长”的假期。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294836}, {"id": 290594, "content": "打开冰箱满满的可乐、啤酒、苏打水、果汁、椰汁、柠檬茶、北冰洋、三得利微醺…当然也有星冰乐啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75414}, {"id": 291618, "content": "每天都是空调让我感受不到夏天的存在，感觉一年里没有夏天???，好无奈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393446}, {"id": 290595, "content": "暑假啊！想干什么干什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390479}, {"id": 290596, "content": "和盆友们粗去玩耍呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068942}, {"id": 290597, "content": "可以吃西瓜！一天半个！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387392}, {"id": 290598, "content": "夏夜公园湖边吹来的风", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390478}, {"id": 290599, "content": "冰淇淋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 290600, "content": "白皙的皮肤", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390485}, {"id": 290601, "content": "白皙的皮肤", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390485}, {"id": 290602, "content": "又是一年毕业季", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390485}, {"id": 290603, "content": "火锅和冰咖啡都是半夜high的助攻神器！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390487}, {"id": 290604, "content": "喝着星冰乐，跟老婆孩子躺在草地上听爵士乐\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390490}, {"id": 290605, "content": "吃西瓜，吃冰棍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1252192}, {"id": 290607, "content": "！！冰淇淋?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390509}, {"id": 290608, "content": "?星爸爸?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669519}, {"id": 290609, "content": "双份意式浓缩", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026074}, {"id": 290610, "content": "期待夏天，因为穿衣服省时间，日照时间长。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383176}, {"id": 290611, "content": "最热的时候是我的生日！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390535}, {"id": 291123, "content": "裙子！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391959}, {"id": 290612, "content": "我唯一期待的就是夏天天热可以出汗，这样，我吃下去的东西就不会让我长胖啦哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191270}]}